m not really going to think about (2021).\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 1002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few years\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 793}, {\"ngram\": \"an international field\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"that quality\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1:44s\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 900}, {\"ngram\": \"a good lane\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not really going to probably help me too much.\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have had really good preparation.\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1092, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"really good preparation\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1091}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I think I am going to have to probably go quicker than that if I want a medal.\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was a pretty solid swim, still slower than I did at trials.\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pretty solid swim\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1206}, {\"ngram\": \"trials\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I think I need to get around that or be a bit quicker if I want to get in around it.\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1330, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I am sure there is plenty of areas I can improve on for the final.\\\"\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1402, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1360}, {\"ngram\": \"areas\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Duncan Scott and Matt Richards are both safely through to the men's 200m freestyle final \\ud83e\\udd1dWe will see them back in the pool tomorrow evening.#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/qoO9ymloiy Looking ahead to the final, Scott expects it to be a tactical battle, even if Popovici has looked the class of the field so far.\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1404, \"end\": 1416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.9913273362707572, \"rank\": 0.004373974849644039, \"text\": \"Duncan Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\"}, {\"begin\": 1421, \"end\": 1434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richards_(footballer,_born_1984)\", \"score\": 0.8167390230814645, \"rank\": 0.2243767313019458, \"text\": \"Matt Richards\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richards_(footballer,_born_1984)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richards_(footballer,_born_1984)\"}, {\"begin\": 1612, \"end\": 1617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"score\": 0.6567214802498964, \"rank\": 0.5227155335335208, \"text\": \"Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the men's 200m freestyle final \\ud83e\\udd1d\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1494}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"a tactical battle\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1650}, {\"ngram\": \"Popovici\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1668}, {\"ngram\": \"the class\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1689}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 1693, \"to\": 1702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And after falling just short in Tokyo, Scott has no intention of letting others dictate the race.\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1746, \"end\": 1751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9938621951218247, \"rank\": 0.0