": 2985, \"to\": 3000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I look at the score there and you would never think in your wildest dreams that it would be 59 seconds to win it.\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the score\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3026}, {\"ngram\": \"your wildest dreams\", \"from\": 3062, \"to\": 3081}, {\"ngram\": \"59 seconds\", \"from\": 3099, \"to\": 3109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I gave it my absolute all.\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3149, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my absolute all\", \"from\": 3133, \"to\": 3148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I executed it as well as I could.\", \"from\": 3150, \"to\": 3183, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not about the end goal, it's about the process.\", \"from\": 3184, \"to\": 3236, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end goal\", \"from\": 3199, \"to\": 3211}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 3224, \"to\": 3235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It does not matter what time it says on the scoreboard, I think in my heart I have already won.\", \"from\": 3237, \"to\": 3332, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what time\", \"from\": 3256, \"to\": 3265}, {\"ngram\": \"the scoreboard\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3291}, {\"ngram\": \"my heart\", \"from\": 3304, \"to\": 3312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am so happy that I can race against the best in the world and still come joint-second.\", \"from\": 3334, \"to\": 3423, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In my heart I have won, these are happy tears.\", \"from\": 3424, \"to\": 3470, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my heart\", \"from\": 3427, \"to\": 3435}, {\"ngram\": \"happy tears\", \"from\": 3458, \"to\": 3469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I gave my absolute best every single day and I cannot be upset about that.\", \"from\": 3471, \"to\": 3545, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\